1/264146.jpg","floor":"#11-1","id":"1245841","time":"2017-6-7 15:16","userId":"264146","userName":"小T","userSign":"","message":"对的，不要搞一堆动画或是艺术字，结尾不要太有创意，重要。<br><br>然后就是尽量没有字吧，放备注自己讲之类的来解决。"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/22/03/220330.jpg","floor":"#12","id":"1245845","time":"2017-6-7 15:32","userId":"messi","userName":"messi","userSign":"","message":"ppt: 左上角标题，右上角校徽，底部论文题目和日期，白底黑字，中文用黑体和宋体，英文用Times New Roman或者Arial，动画效果简洁明了不花哨为宜<br><br>LaTex: 找一个beamer模板","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/09/92/99210.jpg","floor":"#12-1","id":"1245871","time":"2017-6-7 17:40","userId":"skysweetdark","userName":"aja","userSign":"","message":"LaTex超酷的！！！"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/22/03/220330.jpg","floor":"#12-2","id":"1245904","time":"2017-6-7 22:38","userId":"messi","userName":"messi","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">阿良良木翔</span> 说: LaTex超酷的！！！</q></div>表示已放弃PPT，投入TeX的怀抱"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/09/92/99210.jpg","floor":"#12-3","id":"1245905","time":"2017-6-7 22:41","userId":"skysweetdark","userName":"aja","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">messi</span> 说: 表示已放弃PPT，投入TeX的怀抱</q></div>羡慕<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/17.gif\" smileid=\"56\" alt=\"(bgm40)\"><br>简直是奇淫技巧。"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/22/03/220330.jpg","floor":"#12-4","id":"1245907","time":"2017-6-7 23:03","userId":"messi","userName":"messi","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">阿良良木翔</span> 说: 羡慕<br>简直是奇淫技巧。</q></div>学习成本较高，收益爆表，一旦入坑即不能自拔<span style=\"background-color:#555;color:#555;border:1px solid #555;\">（不仅可玩遍各种姿势，还可以定义速度、深度、湿度，玩法还可DIY，，您为什么不来一发呢）</span>"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/17/78/177820.jpg","floor":"#12-5","id":"1245941","time":"2017-6-8 03:14","userId":"franklinyu","userName":"Franklin Yu","userSign":"","message":"LaTeX +1"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/12/77/127728.jpg","f